/p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Fantastic support.\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">A must have for E-commerce!</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/otp1\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/04afeed839e0890f805ab52a1dfd2339?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/04afeed839e0890f805ab52a1dfd2339?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/otp1\" class=\"reviewer-name\">OTP\'Web <small>(otp1)</small></a> on <span class=\"review-date\">February 11, 2021</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">This plugin is a must have for anyone who wants to start E-commerce with WordPress.\n\nAfter testing several solutions under several CMS (including Joomla, Drupal, Prestashop, Contao, etc.) I must say that WooCommerce is much easier to configure and use than anything I tested.\n\nFor those who need advanced features, a multitude of plugins are available and mostly developed by the WooCommerce team itself, like many themes too, a pledge of confidence!</div>\n</div>\n\";}s:13:\"download_link\";s:60:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/woocommerce.5.0.0.zip\";s:11:\"screenshots\";a:6