s=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Fantastic calendar plugin...</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"4 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"4\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/communities\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/5b197bc094a2a28b968a4c5a44ef71c6?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/5b197bc094a2a28b968a4c5a44ef71c6?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/communities\" class=\"reviewer-name\">communities</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">February 28, 2021</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Great calendar\nWould like to improve the danish translation in the ticket part, at the fontend, but i can\'t find the RSPV part in the localization module ...? The RSVP word is not good in danish :-)</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Great Product, GreatSupport!!!!!</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/berobo\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/31596ab506f269fb0e7ffbb6ca705f9c?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/31596ab506f269fb0e7ffbb6ca705f9c?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/berobo\" class=\"reviewer-name\">berobo</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">February 17, 2021</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">This Plugin get the job done, and the support teams help are A++++</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">CSS on every page</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"4 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"4\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/schuerich\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/bbb52306079692dae064cfe17c987868?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/bbb52306079692dae064cfe17c987868?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/schuerich\" class=\"reviewer-name\">schuerich</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">February 14, 2021</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Good calendar without shortcode - no SEO option for a page based on post PHP. But the bigger problem is loading CSS on every page. 100% pages. What is the point and why has such a large company failed to deal with such an important problem? For example, EventON has the option to not load CSS on every page (1 checkbox), but only on pages where the calendar actually appears. There is no shortcode option here, so loading CSS on 100% of pages does not make sense and slows down the entire site. \n\ncommon-skeleton.min.css\ntooltip.min.css</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">ore than 10 months</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"3 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"3\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/maba666\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/443cc8b40857bc00e187b9d42a996ebc?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/443cc8b40857bc00e187b9d42a996ebc?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/maba666\" class=\"reviewer-name\">maba666</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">February 13, 2021</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">More than 10 months after the Google recommendation to add Covid information to the events, there are still no corresponding fields implemented</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Great Plugin It Rocks!</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"4 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"4\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/laspisa33\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/ce0f6a06eb499409770b1abc1a5d452b?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/ce0f6a06eb499409770b1abc1a5d452b?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/laspisa33\" class=\"reviewer-name\">laspisa33</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">February 10, 2021</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">My only very small issue is that not everything is user friendly.  But I love this app and love the flexibility it provides and the options available at not cost.\n\nThank you!</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Simple and wonderful</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/kylemx920\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/8a00a379392d941dc3cbe2af8f384548?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/8a00a379392d941dc3cbe2af8f384548?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/kylemx920\" class=\"reviewer-name\">kylemx920</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">February 3, 2021</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Very happy</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">great support</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/efindlow\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/495195c4f659a5ef4e960030226db61c?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/495195c4f659a5ef4e960030226db61c?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/efindlow\" class=\"reviewer-name\">efindlow</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">February 3, 2021</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">fast response and very helpful</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Easy. Worked out of the box</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/cecileseth\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/e2f282cc0936ce495aae59115235bc9f?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/e2f282cc0936ce495aae59115235bc9f?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/cecileseth\" class=\"reviewer-name\">cecileseth</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">January 28, 2021</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Amazing how much functionality we can get on a free plugin.  Thank you!  6 months later I\'m ready to add RSVP &amp; repeat event functionality.  Thanks for making it modular and easy to upgrade.  </div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Good, but the search is horrible</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"3 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"3\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/coe13\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/ce38f772040a2718ecdc9ef2f5094df9?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/ce38f772040a2718ecdc9ef2f5094df9?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/coe13\" class=\"reviewer-name\">coe13</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">January 27, 2021</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">This plugin is good, but the search function is horrible. Venues and organizers aren\'t included in the search, so if someone enters the name of a venue in the search box (presumably looking for all events at that venue), no results will appear. The developer\'s solution is for you to buy their filter add-on, but that\'s a horrible solution to the problem, especially if you have a large number of venues and/or organizers. There are a number of other minor issues that prevent me from giving a better review, too, but search is the major one that can\'t be easily fixed and the reason why I\'m going to have to find a better solution for my client.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Excellent, thank you</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/armchairphilanthropy\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/c0cd95c7d99455e3b54350d507408799?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/c0cd95c7d99455e3b54350d507408799?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/armchairphilanthropy\" class=\"reviewer-name\">armchairphilanthropy</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">January 26, 2021</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Very happy with the events calendar - with the addition of Community Events, it lets my users submit their own events and run a slick and nice looking calendar online.</div>\n</div>\n\";}s:13:\"download_link\";s:68:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/the-events-calendar.5.4.0.zip\";s:11:\"screenshots\";a:9:{i:1;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:72:\"https://ps.w.org/the-events-calendar/assets/screenshot-1.png?rev=2234716\";s:7:\"caption\";s:21:\"Month View with hover\";}i:2;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:72:\"https://ps.w.org/the-events-calendar/assets/screenshot-2.png?rev=2234716\";s:7:\"caption\";s:12:\"Mobile Views\";}i:3;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:72:\"https://ps.w.org/the-events-calendar/assets/screenshot-3.png?rev=2234716\";s:7:\"caption\";s:12:\"Single event\";}i:4;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:72:\"https://ps.w.org/