ere unable to solve the problem with version 15.9   Very poor</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">There are better Plugins for SEO</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"1 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"1\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/funkycss\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/c50d597e2dbe3b5879572cc3868d12ea?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/c50d597e2dbe3b5879572cc3868d12ea?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/funkycss\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Andreas <small>(funkycss)</small></a> on <span class=\"review-date\">February 22, 2021</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">There are better plugins for SEO out there , and most important not spammy and not bloated as Yoast is,\n\nThere so many years that people are asking when you deactivate the plugin to remove all yoast data from db as this is adding more trouble on new seo plugins.\n\nAlso yesterday there is one more time that yoast had a critical error with wordpress sites, and this is not the first time and shows the real face of pure development and bloat of this company.\n\nNever again Yoast </div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<